


# Using PhpMyAdmin



---

## PhpMyAdmin

We don't need to use the command line all the time!

- Web-interface to manage MySQL databases
- Create, visualize, insert, remove, edit *data*
- written in PHP

&nbsp;

    http://localhost/phpadmin/index.php

---

## Access a database

* Database &rarr; Tables &rarr; Records

